main event: A fishing group observed a bright circular object maneuvering at high altitude in France.
interesting points: The object was estimated to be at about 30,000 feet and was circular in shape.,The object seemed to be revolving or spinning during the observation.,It was very bright, almost blinding to the observers.,The sighting lasted for about 5 minutes before the object suddenly disappeared.,This case was documented in the French Gendarmerie files.
witness description: fishing group from St Gilles Croix de Vie
